5. Use AfterClass annotated tearDown method named as afterClass() to:
Close all the tabs and browsers.


































Following selectors are allowed in this scenario:
. id
• name
• xpath (absolute and relative only, dynamic(axes) xpath is not allowed)
• linkText (partialLinkText is not allowed)

